Text:
&lt;Pick up mic and look at cats on bed&gt;
"When I say INSOM, you say NIA!"
"INSOM!"
&lt;Cats go back to sleep&gt;
&lt;Put down mic and stare at ceiling&gt;

Doc: "Great weight loss and lower BP, Peter!"
Me: "Why didn't you tell me before that diet and exercise works?"
Doc: &lt;unamused stare.&gt;

Everyone else on bikes at 530am at @NYHRC: "goawayitsearly."
Me: &lt;smiling, singing "Defying Gravity."&gt;

It's no wonder I have no friends.

&lt;Softly&gt; "Wow, that was a great Youtube video. Now I'll relax and..."
"WAKE UP AAH! WAKE UP!"
&lt;Autoplay snickers and leaves the room...&gt;
